To run the application
NOTE: 
 - Before running the application, download the json file from yelp and convert it into csv file
 - Place the csv file in "app" folder.

Steps:
1. Navigate to the application folder in the terminal that has run.py file
2. Enter " python run.py " command wihtout quotes in terminal
3. Now the applicaiton will run in browser
4. To access the application hit, http://localhost:5000